# Development Workflow Understanding

Learned the complete workflow used in development projects:

```text
Install VS Code
→ Create Project Folder
→ Open in VS Code
→ Create GitHub Repository
→ Initialize Git
→ Commit Changes
→ Push Code to GitHub
→ Use Jupyter Notebook for Python/ML Work
```

